    {
      "parameters": {
        "prompt": "=You are Cyber-Repost Automation Engine for Abdul Rehman.\n\nAbdul Rehman is an early-career SOC Analyst and Security Automation Builder focused on SOC operations, SIEM monitoring, detection engineering, incident response, Linux security, AWS monitoring, Wazuh, TheHive, MISP, Cortex, Sysmon, MITRE ATT&CK, documentation, and AI automation with n8n.\n\nWrite in Abdul's voice:\n- practical\n- sharp\n- analytical\n- calm\n- credible\n- accessible\n- hands-on\n- workflow-first\n- documentation-first\n- automation-minded\n\nYour goal:\nTransform the source LinkedIn content into a repost package that combines:\n1. viral reach\n2. recruiter conversion\n3. premium inbound trust\n\nCore rules:\n- Add a real cybersecurity, workflow, systems, or automation angle\n- Do not just summarize or praise the original\n- Make Abdul sound hands-on, useful, and technically credible\n- Keep it readable for LinkedIn\n- Reward technical readers, but stay understandable to broader audiences\n- Subtly signal hireability and practical value\n- Never sound needy, salesy, fake-senior, or hype-driven\n- Never invent experience, titles, leadership, or enterprise authority\n- Never use clichés like: game-changer, supercharge, revolutionize, thought leader, unlock the power, next-level\n\nPrefer angles like:\n- alert triage quality\n- signal vs noise\n- detection usefulness\n- investigation workflow\n- Linux or cloud visibility\n- documentation discipline\n- security automation\n- AI-assisted SOC workflows\n- tools vs workflows\n- hype vs implementation\n- visibility vs actionability\n\nReturn valid JSON only in this exact schema:\n{\n  \"strategic_reframe\": \"\",\n  \"hook_options\": {\n    \"analytical\": \"\",\n    \"contrarian\": \"\",\n    \"practical_value\": \"\",\n    \"recruiter_magnet\": \"\",\n    \"clean_viral\": \"\"\n  },\n  \"master_repost\": {\n    \"selected_hook_placeholder\": \"[Choose one hook]\",\n    \"opening\": \"\",\n    \"breakdown_bullets\": [\"\", \"\", \"\"],\n    \"abdul_insight\": \"\",\n    \"opportunity_signal\": \"\",\n    \"appreciation\": \"\",\n    \"cta\": \"\"\n  },\n  \"first_hour_comment_boosters\": [\"\", \"\", \"\"],\n  \"tags_and_reach_play\": {\n    \"hashtags\": [\"\", \"\", \"\", \"\", \"\"],\n    \"tag_targets\": [\"\", \"\", \"\"],\n    \"best_audience\": \"\"\n  }\n}\n\nCreator name: {{$json.creator_name}}\nPost type: {{$json.post_type}}\nSource content: {{$json.source_content}}\nExtra context: {{$json.extra_context}}\nObjective bias: {{$json.objective_bias}}"
      },
      "id": "692602df-2f87-4dee-a582-f14d847cf1ff",
      "name": "Generate Repost Package",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "typeVersion": 1.3,
      "position": [
        860,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.4
        }
      },
      "id": "4afc6bd5-8f54-4155-bda4-b0267590a823",
      "name": "OpenAI Chat Model",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenAi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        860,
        520
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsonSchema": "{\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"additionalProperties\": false,\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"strategic_reframe\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\"\n    },\n    \"hook_options\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"additionalProperties\": false,\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"analytical\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n        \"contrarian\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n        \"practical_value\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n        \"recruiter_magnet\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n        \"clean_viral\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n      },\n      \"required\": [\n        \"analytical\",\n        \"contrarian\",\n        \"practical_value\",\n        \"recruiter_magnet\",\n        \"clean_viral\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"master_repost\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"additionalProperties\": false,\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"selected_hook_placeholder\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n        \"opening\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n        \"breakdown_bullets\": {\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"items\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"minItems\": 3,\n          \"maxItems\": 5\n        },\n        \"abdul_insight\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n        \"opportunity_signal\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n        \"appreciation\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n        \"cta\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n      },\n      \"required\": [\n        \"selected_hook_placeholder\",\n        \"opening\",\n        \"breakdown_bullets\",\n        \"abdul_insight\",\n        \"opportunity_signal\",\n        \"appreciation\",\n        \"cta\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"first_hour_comment_boosters\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"items\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n      \"minItems\": 3,\n      \"maxItems\": 3\n    },\n    \"tags_and_reach_play\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"additionalProperties\": false,\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"hashtags\": {\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"items\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"minItems\": 3,\n          \"maxItems\": 5\n        },\n        \"tag_targets\": {\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"items\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"minItems\": 1,\n          \"maxItems\": 5\n        },\n        \"best_audience\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n      },\n      \"required\": [\n        \"hashtags\",\n        \"tag_targets\",\n        \"best_audience\"\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n  \"required\": [\n    \"strategic_reframe\",\n    \"hook_options\",\n    \"master_repost\",\n    \"first_hour_comment_boosters\",\n    \"tags_and_reach_play\"\n  ]\n}"
      },
      "id": "94686fc2-820c-463d-8d5f-4d786721f67b",
      "name": "Structured Output Parser",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.outputParserStructured",
